r trade cycle with execution, we need `--execute` flag and `PAPER_TRADING=true` 
(default)\n4. Output files:\n   - `trade_signals.json` - signals with market dat
a\n   - `paper_trade_log.json` - executed paper trades (only when `--execute`)\n
  - `paper_trade_sim.json` - output from paper_trade_sim.js\n\nThe task asks for
`tests/e2e/paper_trade_smoke.test.js` that runs one full cycle: market scan → si
gnal → order → PnL update. Run in dry-run/mock mode, assert all output files exi
st and are valid JSON/format.\n\nWait, the task says "dry-run/mock mode" but als
o "market scan → signal → order → PnL update". The full cycle would be:\n1. Run 
