de_sim.js` to get PnL simulation\n\nOr perhaps the smoke test should just run `p
aper_trade_sim.js` which internally runs `live_runner.js` and then adds PnL simu
lation. But that doesn\'t execute trades (no `--execute` flag).\n\nLet me think 
