s markets\n- Signal: live_runner.js generates signals\n- Order: live_runner.js w
ith --execute flag generates paper_trade_log.json\n- PnL update: paper_trade_sim
.js computes P&L\n\nSo the E2E smoke test should:\n1. Run `node live_runner.js -
